Comment: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.01,CN,,0,0,0,,------ OPJP ------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:25.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}弾むような頭から手のひら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:30.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}とんかちなリズム刻んでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:35.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}当たり前が少しずれてたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:41.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}おんなじじゃないから楽しいんじゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:43.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}旧石器時代　大先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}その時から　変わんない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}欲しいものが　あれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:49.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes! この手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:50.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes! 今すぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}I do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:58.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}ありふれた毎日にアイデア
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}ちょっぴり万能感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:04.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}歌う鼻歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:08.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}はずれても笑い飛ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:13.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}明日をもっと自由に作るのさ
Comment: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.01,CN,,0,0,0,,------ OPCN ------
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.64,0:22:25.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}这份悸动　驱动着全身
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.90,0:22:30.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}敲打的旋律　铭刻于心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.56,0:22:35.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}即便不完美
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.74,0:22:41.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}也因有所不同　才更加有趣
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.03,0:22:43.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}旧石器时代　是大前辈
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}从那时起就没有改变
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.12,0:22:48.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}有想要的东西的话
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.38,0:22:49.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes！用这双手
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.65,0:22:50.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}Yes！现在立刻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}自己来创造！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.41,0:22:58.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}每天的各种奇思妙想
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}加上一点小灵感
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.08,0:23:04.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻哼着歌
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.14,0:23:08.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}即便不完美也一笑了之
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.88,0:23:13.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)}更自由地去创造明天
